s=\"aligncenter wp-image-4238\" src=\"http://vnggroup.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vng-15-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"867\" srcset=\"http://vnggroup.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vng-15-768x1024.jpg 768w, http://vnggroup.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vng-15-225x300.jpg 225w, http://vnggroup.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vng-15.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Khép lại buổi tối dã ngoại với tiết mục đốt lửa trại và văn nghệ đặc sắc</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://vnggroup.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vng-9.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4232\" src=\"http://vnggroup.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vng-9-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"488\" srcset=\"http://vnggroup.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vng-9-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://vnggroup.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vng-9-300x225.jpg 300w, http://vnggroup.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vng-9-768x576.jpg 768w, http://vnggroup.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vng-9-200x150.jpg 200w, http://vnggroup.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vng-9-100x75.jpg 100w, http://vnggroup.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vng-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Ghé thăm Làng Văn hóa các dân tộc Việt Nam&nbsp; đã khép lại chuyến dã ngoại CBNV VNG</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>Anh Thư</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                                        <div class=\"social\">\r\n                           <div id=\"fb-root\" class=\" fb_reset\"><div style=\"position: absolute; top: -10000px; height: 0px; width: 0px;\"><div><iframe name=\"fb_xdm_frame_http\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" id=\"fb_xdm_frame_http\" aria-hidden=\"true\" title=\"Facebook Cross Domain Communication Frame\" tabi